private class AsSynchronizedGraph.NoCache
extends java.lang.Object
implements AsSynchronizedGraph.CacheStrategy<V,​E>, java.io.Serializable
Don't use cache for AsSynchronizedGraph's edgesOf, incomingEdgesOf and outgoingEdgesOf methods.
